### React Hook Usage with Exhaustive Dependency Validation

Source: https://github.com/facebook/react/blob/main/compiler/packages/babel-plugin-react-compiler/src/__tests__/fixtures/compiler/exhaustive-deps/exhaustive-deps-allow-nonreactive-stable-types-as-extra-deps.expect.md

